<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得如果能在新年第一天保持好心情，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能順遂地度過一整年嗎？<pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="4" />，如何呀？<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天過得還開心嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />去年的日記本我已經收起來了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天才剛要開始用新的呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我要在新的日記本裡寫滿各種新的回憶！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你一定會幫我，對吧！<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在這樣值得慶祝的節日，<delay8 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我稍微放縱一點，應該也沒關係吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說……吃日式年糕湯的時候，<delay20 />
多吃一個年糕之類的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />經過這麼多事，<delay8 />無論是悲是喜，<delay8 />
新的一年都開始了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年我一定要過得<delay8 />
比去年更加充滿歡笑！<pageBreak />俗話說：「笑口常開福滿門」！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />也一起試試吧！<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
笑一個，<delay8 />笑一個！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00">我是不是該<delay8 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />趁著這個機會，
先決定好今年的目標呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要徹底鑽研<tag a="135" b="8" arg="0xcd00" />這個興趣嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊……<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來做一張美食地圖，
專門介紹<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />好像也很不錯耶！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />
你已經決定好<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年的目標了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>